WEBVTT

00:00.232 --> 00:01.565
Previously, on Beyond...

00:01.600 --> 00:03.324
Shoemacher's chemo pills.

00:03.324 --> 00:04.623
Happy to help in any way I can.

00:04.659 --> 00:06.525
Pleased to hear it.

00:06.561 --> 00:08.627
Dispose of him. Discreetly.

00:08.663 --> 00:12.264
It is so nice to finally meet
one of Holden's friends.

00:12.300 --> 00:14.266
I'm happy you two found each other.

00:14.302 --> 00:17.169
I cherish us, the idea
of you and I, Diane.

00:18.573 --> 00:20.639
Keep your helping hands off Christine!

00:20.675 --> 00:24.310
- I thought I was alone in here.
- You're not alone. I'm Willa.

00:24.345 --> 00:25.885
How did you say you two met again?

00:28.516 --> 00:30.583
- Maybe this was a mistake.
- Maybe it was.

